  "content": "<h1><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Data Description and Preparation</span></h1><p><strong style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Data Description:</strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> The dataset contains </span><strong style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">customer demographic and telecom usage attributes</strong><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">. Key fields include:</span></p><p><strong style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Demographics &amp; Account:</strong></p><ul><li class=\"ql-indent-1\"><code style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">state</code><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">, </span><code style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">account_length</code><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">, </span><code style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">area_code</code><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">, </span><code style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">phone_number</code><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">.</span></li></ul><p><strong style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Plans:</strong></p><ul><li class=\"ql-indent-1\"><code style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">intl_plan</code><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">, </span><code style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">voice_mail_plan</code><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">, </span><code style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">number_vmail_messages</code><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">.</span></li></ul><p><strong style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Usage Metrics:</strong></p><ul><li class=\"ql-indent-1\"><code style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">total_day_minutes</code><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">, </span><code style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">total_day_calls</code><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">, </span><code style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">total_day_charge</code><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">.</span></li><li class=\"ql-indent-1\"><code style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">total_eve_minutes</code><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">, </span><code style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">total_eve_calls</code><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">, </span><code style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">total_eve_charge</code><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">.</span></li><li class=\"ql-indent-1\"><code style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">total_night_minutes</code><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">, </span><code style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">total_night_calls</code><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">, </span><code style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">total_night_charge</code><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">.</span></li><li class=\"ql-indent-1\"><code style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">total_intl_minutes</code><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">, </span><code style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">total_intl_calls</code><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">, </span><code style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">total_intl_charge</code><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">.</span></li></ul><p><strong style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Support Interaction:</strong></p><ul><li class=\"ql-indent-1\"><code style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">number_customer_service_calls</code><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">.</span></li></ul><p><strong style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Target Variable:</strong></p><ul><li class=\"ql-indent-1\"><code style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">churned</code><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> (Yes/No → after cleaning formatting issues).</span></li></ul><p><strong style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Data Preparation Steps:</strong></p><p>\t<strong style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">1.Cleaning:</strong></p><ul><li class=\"ql-indent-1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Remove special characters in the </span><code style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">churned</code><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> column.</span></li><li class=\"ql-indent-1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Handle missing values (if any) in usage and account features.</span></li></ul><p>\t<strong style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">2.Feature Engineering:</strong></p><ul><li class=\"ql-indent-1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Compute </span><strong style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">total_charges</strong><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> = </span><code style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">day_charge + eve_charge + night_charge + intl_charge</code><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">.</span></li><li class=\"ql-indent-1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Compute </span><strong style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">total_minutes</strong><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> = sum of all minutes (day, evening, night, international).</span></li><li class=\"ql-indent-1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Derive </span><strong style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">domestic_usage</strong><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> (total minutes – international minutes).</span></li><li class=\"ql-indent-1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Categorize </span><code style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">account_length</code><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> into </span><strong style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Account_Length_Groups</strong><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> for better analysis.</span></li></ul><p>\t<strong style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">3.Encoding:</strong></p><ul><li class=\"ql-indent-1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Convert categorical fields (</span><code style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">intl_plan</code><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">, </span><code style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">voice_mail_plan</code><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">, </span><code style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">state</code><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">) into numerical representations.</span></li></ul><p>\t<strong style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">4.Balancing Data:</strong></p><ul><li class=\"ql-indent-1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">If churn classes are imbalanced, apply </span><strong style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">class weights</strong><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> or oversampling methods (e.g., SMOTE).</span></li></ul>",
